That's the good news.

224
00:11:36,710 --> 00:11:41,880
The bad news is that how do you
make a system safer than this?

225
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:45,440
How do you address the more
complex and interrelated

226
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,560
