227
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:49,490
For this, I would
put out that you

228
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:52,460
have to do many things
all at the same time.

229
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:55,490
As engineers, we
normally start by looking

230
00:11:55,490 --> 00:11:58,610
