pilot doesn't have the fan disk

237
00:12:15,860 --> 00:12:17,480
blow apart in the first place--

238
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:21,910
necessary, but again,
not sufficient.

239
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:24,280
And finally, we
find that we have

240
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:29,090
