00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:46,260
control the situation right
at the point of the incident,

247
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:48,420
of the problem--

248
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:51,340
the pointy end of the stick.

249
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:54,980
Now there's multiple
layers of control.

